     FBRIDF     IF   E           K DISK    USROPN
     FSVIH      IF   E           K DISK    USROPN
     FCUNDL01   IF   E           K DISK    USROPN
KING FKUNDL01   IF   E           K DISK    USROPN
KING F                                     PREFIX(X_)
KING F                                     RENAME(KUNDR:KUNDRX)
