      * Varible for
     D WSUSER          S             10
     D AVD             S              4
     D AVDN            S              4  0
     D OPD             S              7
     D OPDN            S              7  0
     D WBIT1           C                   CONST('Y040')
     D WBIT2           C                   CONST('Y041')
     D WBII1           S             35
     D WBII2           S             35
     D JSONstring      s          32000
     D Error           S            150
     D AntLest         S              9  0

      *get input-string
      /copy syspeds/qrpgsrcpy,prolog3

      * Parse input
     C                   exsr      Parse
      * Open files etc
     C                   EXSR      INIT
      *
     c                   callp     gethtmlifs(
