      * Quit
     C                   exsr      Exit


      *=====================================================================
      * Close output html and quit
      *=====================================================================
     C     Exit          begsr
      * Lukk fil
     C                   CLOSE     BRIDF
     C  N50              CLOSE     SVIH
     C  N50              CLOSE     CUNDL01
     C  N50              CLOSE     KUNDL01

      * Do not delete the call to wrtsection with section name *fini.  It is needed
